{"tid":456932,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"看護遭性騷擾 用笑面對人生","createTime":"2017-11-03T10:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T07:23:34.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a55228ecb913a19acf556b390e416fe9f3174789","tid":456932,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"普遍人對老人看護的想像都是「人工低」「辛苦」「工時長」等等，再加上越來越多看護遭性騷擾的事件，自然就沒有人願意投身這個行業。上星期在AbemaTV播出的《Wの悲喜劇～日本一過激なオンナのニュース～》，幾位看護分享這份工作的美好之處。<br />\n<br />\n想知道護相關的現況？大家可以先回一點小帶，看看這篇：看護不是奴隸。<br />\n<br />\n對一般人而言，遭性騷擾會感到不安、嘔心，<span style=\"color: red;\">但美女看護上条百里奈小姐卻不會生氣，反而讓老人觸摸自己。</span><br />\n<br />\n她說：「如果動怒的話，就沒有資格自稱專業人士。例如，<span style=\"color: red;\">試過有一位伯伯跟我說『無論如何都想摸妳的胸』，因為他左手麻痺，所以我就跟他說『如果用左手的話，可以喔～』。</span>本來他完全沒有打算做物理治療，但那天突然間很努力，嘗試令左手動起來。如果因為我幾句說話，就能讓他們獲得生存下去的動力或勇氣，我就覺得足夠了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=6421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D6421&d=tMGIoADtvKaCLio6ApwBwjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a347ef2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=6421</a>"},{"pid":"6fc551d97383dded3917cfb992cba1c024868b03","tid":456932,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.news.livedoor.com/newsimage/stf/1/a/1a6fe_1585_ec24d6bf34cb49abe73d09c65168e6f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.news.livedoor.com%2Fnewsimage%2Fstf%2F1%2Fa%2F1a6fe_1585_ec24d6bf34cb49abe73d09c65168e6f9.jpg&h=1fea9bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n